@UtilityHub360_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Health Check
GET {{UtilityHub360_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Weather Forecast (Test Endpoint)
GET {{UtilityHub360_HostAddress}}/api/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Loan Details
GET {{UtilityHub360_HostAddress}}/api/Loans/YOUR_LOAN_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Loan Payment Schedule
GET {{UtilityHub360_HostAddress}}/api/Loans/YOUR_LOAN_ID/schedule
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Add Payment Schedule (Custom Installments)
POST {{UtilityHub360_HostAddress}}/api/Loans/YOUR_LOAN_ID/add-schedule
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "startingInstallmentNumber": 13,
  "numberOfMonths": 3,
  "firstDueDate": "2024-07-15T00:00:00Z",
  "monthlyPayment": 1200.00,
  "reason": "Adding additional payments"
}

###

### Extend Loan Term
POST {{UtilityHub360_HostAddress}}/api/Loans/YOUR_LOAN_ID/extend-term
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "additionalMonths": 6,
  "reason": "Extension needed"
}

###

### Update Payment Schedule
PATCH {{UtilityHub360_HostAddress}}/api/Loans/YOUR_LOAN_ID/schedule/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 900.00,
  "status": "PAID",
  "paymentMethod": "CASH"
}

###
